.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/he-thong-i-clc-dau-tu-dong-bo-hon-100-man-hinh-tuong-tac-innosmart-dan-dau-trong-chuyen-doi-so-giang-day-ngoai-ngu-tai-viet-nam\/#i-clc_doi_moi_voi_mo_hinh_lop_hoc_hien_dai\" >I-CLC \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/he-thong-i-clc-dau-tu-dong-bo-hon-100-man-hinh-tuong-tac-innosmart-dan-dau-trong-chuyen-doi-so-giang-day-ngoai-ngu-tai-viet-nam\/#ung_dung_innosmart_trong_giang_day_ngoai_ngu_thong_minh\" >\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng INNOSMART trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef th\u00f4ng minh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/he-thong-i-clc-dau-tu-dong-bo-hon-100-man-hinh-tuong-tac-innosmart-dan-dau-trong-chuyen-doi-so-giang-day-ngoai-ngu-tai-viet-nam\/#innosmart_dong_hanh_cung_i-clc_tren_hanh_trinh_dan_dau_doi_moi_giao_duc\" >INNOSMART \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng I-CLC tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ng\u00e0y nay \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef, l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ef1c quan, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, tr\u1ef1c quan v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, INNOSMART c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecdc sinh m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em t\u1ef1 tin r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_16732\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16732\" style=\"width: 900px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/0000001-1.webp\" alt=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng I-CLC \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART - d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" width=\"900\" height=\"677\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16732\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef I-CLC \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh INNOSMART t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Minh Khai<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"i-clc_doi_moi_voi_mo_hinh_lop_hoc_hien_dai\"><\/span>I-CLC \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t tri\u1ec3n khai h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh INNOSMART \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap I-CLC t\u1ea1o ra b\u01b0\u1edbc thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t trong m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Chu\u1ea9n h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li>Gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp cho h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean nh\u1edd m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp th\u00fa v\u1ecb.<\/li>\n<li>N\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y khi gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 tr\u1ef1c quan \u0111\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>I-CLC ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, nh\u1eb1m x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho h\u1ecdc sinh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef I-CLC \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART v\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Minh Khai v\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc \u0110\u1eb7ng Th\u00f9y Tr\u00e2m.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_16731\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-16731\" style=\"width: 900px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/0000001-2.webp\" alt=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng I-CLC \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART - d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" width=\"900\" height=\"678\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-16731\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef I-CLC \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh INNOSMART t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc \u0110\u1eb7ng Thu\u1ef3 Tr\u00e2m<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ung_dung_innosmart_trong_giang_day_ngoai_ngu_thong_minh\"><\/span>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng INNOSMART trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef th\u00f4ng minh<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c quan: Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh c\u00f9ng tham gia gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, t\u0103ng t\u00ednh k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i.<\/li>\n<li>Kho h\u1ecdc li\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 phong ph\u00fa: T\u00edch h\u1ee3p d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng video, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef, b\u00e0i t\u1eadp nh\u00f3m.<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m: Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u00f3m v\u00e0 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111a thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb: Linh ho\u1ea1t tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed9i dung t\u1eeb laptop, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed7i ti\u1ebft h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef tr\u1edf n\u00ean sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"innosmart_dong_hanh_cung_i-clc_tren_hanh_trinh_dan_dau_doi_moi_giao_duc\"><\/span>INNOSMART \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng I-CLC tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART, I-CLC kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf ti\u00ean phong trong \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9ng minh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. INNOSMART \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u cho h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/0000001.webp\" alt=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng I-CLC \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART - d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" width=\"900\" height=\"677\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ng\u00e0y nay \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef, l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ef1c quan, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n 100 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 quan&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":16730,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-16729","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16729","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=16729"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16729\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":16735,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16729\/revisions\/16735"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16730"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=16729"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=16729"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=16729"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}